The '''Taris Holofeed''' was one of the primary news sources on the planet [[Taris/Legends|Taris]] during the time of the [[Mandalorian Wars]]. It included planetary, as well as galactic news. It was based in a [[Highpoint]] office destroyed during the [[Taris Siege|invasion of Taris]].

